h2. Release Notes - Karaf - Version 2.2.0

This release of Apache Karaf contains a multitude of new features, improvements, and bug fixes.  Some highlights include many new or updated commands, a LDAP JAAS module with login support, an updated feature service, a feature for Aries transaction, JPA & JNDI modules, expanded documentation, and new versions of most dependencies. For more detail please see the change log below.

